text: Karl Steiner (born 12 January 1906, date of death unknown) was an Austrian diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Austrian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Austria Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
